quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  39,1,"Tanzeelu alkitabi mina AllahialAAazeezi alhakeem"
  39,2,"Inna anzalna ilayka alkitababilhaqqi faAAbudi Allaha mukhlisanlahu addeen"
  39,3,"Ala lillahi addeenualkhalisu wallatheena ittakhathoomin doonihi awliyaa ma naAAbuduhum illaliyuqarriboona ila Allahi zulfa innaAllaha yahkumu baynahum fee ma hum feehiyakhtalifoona inna Allaha la yahdee man huwa kathibunkaffar"
  39,4,"Law arada Allahu an yattakhithawaladan lastafa mimma yakhluqu mayashao subhanahu huwa Allahu alwahidualqahhar"
  39,5,"Khalaqa assamawati wal-ardabilhaqqi yukawwiru allayla AAala annahariwayukawwiru annahara AAala allayliwasakhkhara ashshamsa walqamara kullun yajreeli-ajalin musamman ala huwa alAAazeezu alghaffar"